<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <title>About | Retro Pizzeria</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css">
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Verdana', sans-serif; /* Clean retro font */
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background-color: #eaf7f7; /* Soft teal background */
    }

    main {
      padding: 30px;
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: 50px auto;
      background-color: #ffe8c2; /* Warm cream background */
      box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
      border-radius: 15px;
      border: 4px solid #e63946; /* Muted red border */
      text-align: center;
    }

    h2 {
      color: #e63946; /* Muted red */
      font-size: 32px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 2px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    p {
      font-size: 18px;
      color: #4a342e; /* Dark brown for retro text */
      margin: 15px 0;
      line-height: 1.6; /* Improve readability */
    }

    .grid-container {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr)); /* Responsive grid */
      gap: 20px;
      margin-top: 30px;
    }

    .grid-item {
      background-color: #f4a261; /* Mustard yellow */
      color: #fff; /* White text for contrast */
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 6px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
      transition: transform 0.3s, box-shadow 0.3s;
    }

    .grid-item:hover {
      transform: translateY(-5px); /* Lift effect on hover */
      box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
    }

    footer {
      margin-top: 40px;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #4a342e; /* Dark brown for footer */
      text-align: center;
    }

    /* Decorative divider for retro flair */
    .divider {
      height: 4px;
      width: 100px;
      background-color: #f4a261; /* Mustard yellow */
      margin: 20px auto;
      border-radius: 2px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <%- include('partials/header') %>
  <main>
    <h2>About Us</h2>
    <div class="divider"></div>
    <p>Welcome to Retro Pizzeria! We serve the best pizzas in town with a retro twist.</p>
    <p>Our pizzas are made with fresh ingredients, authentic recipes, and a whole lot of love. From classic Margherita to bold and adventurous flavors, we’ve got something for everyone.</p>
    <p>Join us for a slice of nostalgia and a taste of perfection. Whether you’re dining in or taking out, Retro Pizzeria is here to make your day better, one pizza at a time.</p>

    <!-- Cool Grid Section -->
    <div class="grid-container">
      <div class="grid-item">
        <h3>Margherita</h3>
        <p>A timeless classic with fresh mozzarella, tangy tomato sauce, and basil leaves.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid-item">
        <h3>Pepperoni</h3>
        <p>The all-time favorite—loaded with spicy pepperoni and gooey cheese.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid-item">
        <h3>BBQ Chicken</h3>
        <p>Smoky BBQ sauce, tender chicken, and a sprinkle of red onions.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid-item">
        <h3>Veggie Supreme</h3>
        <p>A colorful mix of bell peppers, olives, mushrooms, and onions.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid-item">
        <h3>Hawaiian</h3>
        <p>Sweet and savory with juicy pineapple and smoky ham.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid-item">
        <h3>Meat Lovers</h3>
        <p>A hearty pizza topped with sausage, bacon, pepperoni, and ham.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
  <footer>
    <p>&copy; 2025 Retro Pizzeria. Serving nostalgia by the slice since 1985!</p>
  </footer>
  <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>
